    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "## 4. Evaluate the Learned Policy\n\nSimulate the trained controller and compare with the uncontrolled (damped free-swing) pendulum.",
      "metadata": {}
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "/* Simulate trained policy */\nw1_opt : cem_mu[1]$  w2_opt : cem_mu[2]$  w3_opt : cem_mu[3]$\nu_opt : max(-u_max, min(u_max,\n  w1_opt * sin(theta) + w2_opt * cos(theta) + w3_opt * omega))$\nrhs1_opt : omega$\nrhs2_opt : -(gv/lp)*sin(theta) - bp*omega + u_opt/(mp*lp^2)$\n\ntspan_eval : np_linspace(0, 10, 500)$\ntraj_opt : np_cvode([rhs1_opt, rhs2_opt], [t, theta, omega],\n                     [float(%pi), 0.0], tspan_eval, 1e-8, 1e-8)$\n\n/* Uncontrolled pendulum */\ntraj_free : np_cvode([omega, -(gv/lp)*sin(theta) - bp*omega],\n                      [t, theta, omega],\n                      [float(%pi), 0.0], tspan_eval, 1e-8, 1e-8)$\n\nt_eval : np_to_list(np_slice(traj_opt, all, 0))$\nth_opt_list : np_to_list(np_slice(traj_opt, all, 1))$\nth_free_list : np_to_list(np_slice(traj_free, all, 1))$\n\n/* Convert radians to degrees (unwrapped to avoid discontinuities at ±180°) */\nto_deg(a) := a * 180 / float(%pi)$\n\nax_draw2d(\n  line_width = 2,\n  color = royalblue,\n  name = \"CEM policy\",\n  lines(t_eval, map(to_deg, th_opt_list)),\n  color = \"#aaa\",\n  dash = \"dash\",\n  name = \"Uncontrolled\",\n  lines(t_eval, map(to_deg, th_free_list)),\n  title = \"Pendulum Swing-Up: CEM vs Uncontrolled\",\n  xlabel = \"Time (s)\",\n  ylabel = \"theta (deg)\",\n  grid = true\n)$",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": 64,
      "outputs": [
