      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "/* Simulate higher-torque policy */\nw1_2 : cem_mu2[1]$  w2_2 : cem_mu2[2]$  w3_2 : cem_mu2[3]$\nu_2 : max(-u_max, min(u_max,\n  w1_2 * sin(theta) + w2_2 * cos(theta) + w3_2 * omega))$\n\ntraj2 : np_cvode([omega, -(gv/lp)*sin(theta) - bp*omega + u_2/(mp*lp^2)],\n                  [t, theta, omega],\n                  [float(%pi), 0.0], tspan_eval, 1e-8, 1e-8)$\n\nt2 : np_to_list(np_slice(traj2, all, 0))$\nth2 : np_to_list(np_slice(traj2, all, 1))$\nom2 : np_to_list(np_slice(traj2, all, 2))$\n\nax_draw2d(\n  line_width = 2,\n  color = royalblue,\n  name = \"u_max = 12\",\n  lines(t2, map(to_deg, th2)),\n  color = \"#aaa\",\n  dash = \"dash\",\n  name = \"Uncontrolled\",\n  lines(t_eval, map(to_deg, th_free_list)),\n  title = \"Swing-Up with Higher Torque\",\n  xlabel = \"Time (s)\",\n  ylabel = \"theta (deg)\",\n  grid = true\n)$",
