    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "/* Simulate improved policy */\nw1_3 : cem_mu3[1]$  w2_3 : cem_mu3[2]$  w3_3 : cem_mu3[3]$\nu_3 : max(-u_max, min(u_max,\n  w1_3 * sin(theta) + w2_3 * (1 - cos(theta)) + w3_3 * omega))$\n\ntraj3 : np_cvode([omega, -(gv/lp)*sin(theta) - bp*omega + u_3/(mp*lp^2)],\n                  [t, theta, omega],\n                  [float(%pi), 0.0], tspan_eval, 1e-8, 1e-8)$\n\nt3 : np_to_list(np_slice(traj3, all, 0))$\nth3 : np_to_list(np_slice(traj3, all, 1))$\nom3 : np_to_list(np_slice(traj3, all, 2))$\n\n/* Plot angular error from upright: acos(cos(theta)) is always in [0, pi],\n   giving shortest angular distance to the nearest upright position. */\nerr_deg(a) := acos(cos(a)) * 180 / float(%pi)$\n\nax_draw2d(\n  line_width = 2,\n  color = royalblue,\n  name = \"Improved policy\",\n  lines(t3, map(err_deg, th3)),\n  color = \"#aaa\",\n  dash = \"dash\",\n  name = \"Uncontrolled\",\n  lines(t_eval, map(err_deg, th_free_list)),\n  title = \"Angular Error from Upright\",\n  xlabel = \"Time (s)\",\n  ylabel = \"Error (deg)\",\n  grid = true\n)$",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": 70,
